160
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:41,520
[An obsession, a thought,
a fleeting life.]

161
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:45,170
[A sorrow, a joy, and a regret.]

162
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:46,860
[Life is like a dream.]

163
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:49,070
